## Django Commands

### Development

```bash
# Run development server
python manage.py runserver

# Create migrations
python manage.py makemigrations

# Apply migrations
python manage.py migrate

# Create superuser
python manage.py createsuperuser

# Collect static files
python manage.py collectstatic
```

### Management Commands

{% for app in apps %}
